Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--------------------------------------------------Avant--------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.65,0:00:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,原來有這麼多樂器啊
